<br />
<br />Get a Videomation CPROM cart, which does exactly that with 16KB of CHR-RAM, and replace the ROM with something writable.  Of course, 32KB of PRG-ROM isn't much to work with these days, so you may wish to use the extra lines on the '161 to increase the PRG-ROM up to 128KB, ala BNROM.  Even still you won't be creating Grand Theftendo with such a cart.</div>

